snippet: The woman, who once claimed to have had sex with Senator Robert Menendez of New Jersey, swears she never met him, a lawyer said.
abstract: Nexis de los Santos, Dominican woman who said in a video that she had sex with Sen Robert Menendez of New Jersey for money is now acknowledging that the story is false, and that she has never met him.
